title: Print, "Calendar Page: May 1930", 1930
markings: Imprinted on plate, lower left: stadsbrukk erij; at lower right: H. Th. Wijdeveld
description: Dutch calendar page with "1930" imprinted at upper left and upper right; "Mei" at upper center above a grid with dates arranged in vertical rows.  Names of days in Dutch at left and right sides.  At bottom, a secondary dated grid with space for notes.

tombstone.epitaph:
Print, "Calendar Page: May 1930", 1930.
1930. Lithograph on cream wove paper. Gift of Tamar Cohen. 1999-6-3.
